question: What is the name of the main square in Leeuwarden, Netherlands where the market is held every Friday?
asked_question_translated: Apa nama alun-alun utama di Leeuwarden, Belanda yang menjadi lokasi pasar setiap hari Jumat?
answer: Nama alun-alun utama di Leeuwarden, Belanda yang menjadi lokasi pasar setiap hari Jumat adalah Wilhelminaplein.
answer_translated_eng: The name of the main square in Leeuwarden, Netherlands where the market is held every Friday is Wilhelminaplein.
